auditorium.loganalysis

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • auditorium.loganalysis.Graph

  • public class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a log file, generate a visual dag of the messages and print a statistics file. The main takes a list of files to generate statistics about -- for each file A, A.pdf and A.stat will be generated. The pdf is the graphviz generated visual DAG, and the stat file gives you some interesting statistics.
